     H            Y.                                    1
     FMTAPP01 IF  E           K        DISK
     FMFAPL25 IF  E           K        DISK
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80W1DTHZ
     I                                        1   40W1DTYY
     I                                        5   60W1DTMM
     I                                        7   80W1DTDD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80K@SDAT
     I                                        1   40K@YY
     I                                        5   60K@MM
     I                                        7   80K@DD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   4 M@SYS1
     I                                        1   2 M@SYSA
     I                                        3   4 M@SYSB
     I            DS
     I                                        1  20 K@MSNN
     I                                        1   2 K@SYSA
     I                                        3   3 K@HF
     I                                        4   5 K@SYSB
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P@SDAT  80       IN
     C                     PARM           P@EDAT  80       IN
     C                     PARM           P@KIBN  3        IN
      *
     C                     PARM           P@OUTS 100       OUT
     C                     PARM           P@HOUR 100       OUT
     C                     PARM           P@RPMH  60       OUT (PRODUCTIVITY)
      *
     C                     Z-ADDP@SDAT    K@SDAT  80
     C                     Z-ADDP@EDAT    K@EDAT  80
     C                     MOVE P@KIBN    K@KIBN  3
      *
     C                     Z-ADD0         P@OUTS
     C                     Z-ADD0         P@HOUR
     C                     Z-ADD0         P@RPMH
      *
     C                     Z-ADD0111      M6BMON
     C                     EXSR #MFA
     C           M@SYS1    IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     GOTO @END
     C                     END
      *
     C                     MOVE M@SYSA    K@SYSA
     C                     MOVE '-'       K@HF
     C                     MOVE M@SYSB    K@SYSB
      *
     C           KEY       KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K@MSNN 20
     C                     KFLD           K@YY    40
     C                     KFLD           K@MM    20
     C                     KFLD           K@DD    20
      *
     C           KY2       KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K@MSNN 20
      *
     C                     Z-ADD0         W#WATM 100
     C                     Z-ADD0         W#WATK 100
     C                     Z-ADD0         W#WATT 100
      *
     C           KEY       SETLLMTAPP01
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C           KY2       READEMTAPP01                  77
     C   77                LEAVE
      *
     C           W1DTHZ    IFGT K@EDAT
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     END
      *
     C                     ADD  M1OUTS    P@OUTS
     C                     ADD  M1HOUR    P@HOUR
      *
     C                     ADD  M1WATM    W#WATM
     C                     ADD  M1WATK    W#WATK
     C                     ADD  M1WATT    W#WATT
      *
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     Z-ADD0         W#TOTL 100
     C                     ADD  W#WATM    W#TOTL
     C                     ADD  W#WATK    W#TOTL
     C                     ADD  W#WATT    W#TOTL
      *
     C           W#TOTL    DIV  60        W#WOTM 100H
      *
     C                     SUB  W#WOTM    P@HOUR
      *
     C           P@HOUR    IFNE 0
     C           P@OUTS    DIV  P@HOUR    P@RPMH    H
     C                     ELSE
     C                     Z-ADD1         P@RPMH
     C                     END
      *
     C           @END      TAG
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
     C*-----------------------------------------------------
     C           #MFA      BEGSR
      *
     C           MFAKEY    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           M6BMON  40
     C                     KFLD           K@KIBN
     C* * *                KFLD           W@AKT
      *
     C           MFAKEY    SETLLMFAPL25
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C           MFAKEY    READEMFAPL25                  44
     C   44                LEAVE
     C           M@SKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C                     ITER
     C                     END
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C           *IN44     IFEQ '1'
     C                     Z-ADD0         M@RPMH
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    M@SYS1
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    M@SYS2
     C                     END
      *
     C           EMFA      ENDSR
      *
